<template>
  <GChart
    :settings="{ packages: ['geochart'] }"
    type="GeoChart"
    :data="chartData"
    :options="chartOptions"
    ref="gChart"
  />
</template>
<script>
import { GChart } from "vue-google-charts";

export default {
  name: "geochart",
  components: {
    GChart,
  },
  data() {
    return {
      chartData: [["Country","Volume"],
["SA",317437]
,["US",32203]
,["FR",447]
,["Germany",25690]
,["Kazakhstan",5895]
,["Jordan",1537300],
["Dominican Republic",2411]
,["Bolivia",886],
["United Arab Emirates",1429],
["Brazil",760]
,["India",4987]],

      chartOptions: {
        // region: "145",
        height: 600,
        

        datalessRegionColor: "gray",
        colorAxis: {
          colors: ["#7ef9c0", "#088d4f"],
        },
        backgroundColor: "#799ed5",
        displayMode: "auto",
        // forceIFrame:true,
        keepAspectRatio: false,
        // enableRegionInteractivity:false,
      },
    };
  },
};
</script>
